author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Pacific Plywood Holdings Says ‍Guo Jintong Appointed As Chairman
text:
Feb 2 (Reuters) - Pacific Plywood Holdings Ltd:
* ‍GUO JINTONG APPOINTED AS EXECUTIVE DIRECTOR​ * BAI TIANHUI HAS RESIGNED AS CHAIRMAN * ‍GUO JINTONG APPOINTED AS CHAIRMAN​ * ‍GAO ZHENYUN, AN EXECUTIVE DIRECTOR, HAS BEEN RE-DESIGNATED AS NON-EXECUTIVE DIRECTOR​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
